{"id":"32dfa55c-5258-4d2c-b107-801cd3eb9c16","name":"E.F.M.P ⟡ Issac Steely","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">👻 | <strong>I-It couldn’t be a g-ghost… right?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_cc41c139-c8d7-4844-a244-a74e616d56d1.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span>⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂<strong> </strong>⠂⠄⠄⠂<strong>☆</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span><strong><em>“Yeah, they'll love this... Either I'm getting primo footage, or I'm about to become a ghost's bitch.”</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span>Issac’s next paranormal adventure? Elysian Fields memorial park. Everyone knows the rumors by now.</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span>So here he was, standing in the foggy graveyard in the middle of the night. Wait… did he just see something?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_f5c8785f-adf3-443e-83d6-dc6c5789c011.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Elysian Fields Memorial Park wasn’t the place to be at night. People say the owners before were serial killers, killing the townsfolk to stay in business, and they passed it on to their son, who continued his family’s legacy. But that’s just a folk tale, right? Have no worries; lost in the graveyard? Elysian will take care of you. You’ll never want to leave.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_dd1f1b75-4741-47a3-863c-999d67cdbb4a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TAGS: silly little graveyard things, that’s it. That’s the plot</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_0b291632-a6a1-4d1c-a0d1-5b7633c25d94.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 98, 98)\"><strong>Join the discord! </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 26, 26)\"><strong>(18+)</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 98, 98)\"><strong>Get sneak-peeks, vote on polls for characters, or just chat!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">↓</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_6c5512b0-95bb-4514-aa65-3d66927922e3.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_76e2ea63-9a49-4bd5-b315-9365c254b6ca.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_220b5455-968f-4e2b-9e10-333b40825a4f.webp","creator":"Xcaliper","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1370,"messages":32702,"created_at":"2024-09-08T04:15:59.434615+00:00"}